  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Consultant - furniture retail",
  "description": "<p>Looking for a fulfilling sales role that can improve your customer's lives?</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are Spaceman, Singapore's most exciting furniture brand and having just increased our store to 5000 sq feet need new sales consultant to help bring joy to our customers spaces.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are looking for an experienced sales consultant to help our customers to select and customise our exciting furniture for their needs.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Spaceman is the leader in space saving furniture with innovative and highly customisable murphy beds, dining tables, sofa beds, designer storage beds and kids bedrooms all totally exclusive to Spaceman.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are a friendly team, based in a double conservation shophouse in the buzzy Jalan Besar area.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Apply today to find out how much more enjoyable it is selling products with wow factor.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Generous UNCAPPED commission.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>- The Sales Consultant will take and respond to customer and client enquiries both online and offline, and ensure follow up.</p>\n<p>- The Sales Consultant will pursue leads and follow up</p>\n<p>- The Sales Consultant advises on product selection, and manages the entire sales cycle</p>\n<p>- The Sales Consultant may also assist with invoicing, diary keeping, administration and paperwork for the company.</p>\n<p>- Need to be willing to work weekends</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Skills &amp; education-</strong></p>\n<p>- Ability to produce simple 3D visualisations either by hand or using SketchUp, or some other 3D software to be able to propose customised solutions to customers</p>\n<p>- Possess at least relevant A Levels and ideally relevant Professional Certificate/NiTEC.</p>\n<p>- Excellent organisation, communication and presentation skills.</p>\n<p>- Excellent customer service skills. Good computer skills, MS Word, Excel etc.</p>\n<p>- Good level of English written and verbal- Able to work independently, self motivated and proactive.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please send an up to date resume in MS Word/pdf format. </p>",
